title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Doubled Passive Income from the Garment Factory
content:
Aside from serving as the nerve center of your Agents of Sabotage operations, the Darnell Bros Garment Factory (30% off this week) will also bring in doubled Passive Income through May 21, which you can claim from the Wall Safe upstairs. GTA+ Members can fill their coffers extra quick this week with 4X Passive Income.

Keep track of your headway and potential rewards from Agents of Sabotage in Career Progress.
